QuestData.Title: More Effort, More Reward
QuestData.Description:
We're not sad. We're starving. |L303-That's the truth of it.|l A few tasty roots won't |L303-be enough.|l
Elder Mhaz doesn't recognize strength, but I do. It should be |L303(100)-trivial|l for you to bring us some fresh meat! The |L303-worms to the east should be easy prey|l.
Please, bring back |L303-what you can carry!|l
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa pieces of meat from worms.
